title: Fairy Cakes
description: Vegan bakery opened 2012 and as of summer 2015 it's sharing a storefront with Chomp Vegan Eatery. Offers cupcakes and baked goods made with organic and fair-trade ingredients as possible. Everything is peanut-free and nut-free. Also offers elf loaves: savory vegan ham and cheese, vegan seafood and garlic, tomato and basil. Specialty decorating, catering, and delivery available.
